<node CREATED="1738341998088" MODIFIED="1738341998088" TEXT="Background        Education to live together emphasizes social harmony, unity in diversity, and building a cohesive society. It aims to promote mutual respect, tolerance, and understanding among diverse cultural, religious, and social groups in India"/>
